    GetVertexCount
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>GetVertexCount</TypeRef> method returns the number of vertices accessible through this vertex attribute.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[size_t GetVertexCount() const;]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Return value">
      <ReturnValue Type="size_t">
        The number of vertices described by this vertex attribute.
      </ReturnValue>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
